ElementDescription: PSQI Total score
Notes: Modified score: psqi_total_score  = Sum of Components 1 to 7; Component 1 (Subjective sleep quality) score = csq_psqi_6 score; Component 2 (Sleep latency) score: 0 = sum csq_psqi_2_score + csq_psqi_5a_score is 0; 1 = sum is 1-2, 2 = sum is 3-4, 3 = sum is 5-6;  Component 3 (Sleep duration) score = csq_psqi_4 score; Component 4 (Sleep efficiency) score: 0 = sleep efficiency greater than 85%, 1 = 75-84%, 2 = 65-74%, 3 = less than 65%; Component 5 (Sleep disturbance) score: 0 = sum csq_psqi_5b1_score + csq_psqi_5b2_score is 0; 1 = sum is 1-2, 2 = sum is 3-4, 3 = sum is 5-6; Component 6 (Use of sleeping medication) score = csq_psqi_7 score; Component 7 (Daytime dsyfunction) score = csq_psqi_8 score
